    "attributes": {
        "action": "refund 2 months Road tax for every car driver, due to the amount of pot holes",
        "additional_details": "In order to address this situation I believe that the government should reduce the amount of road tax for next year as compensation or give back the equivalent of two months road tax to every car owner in the country.\r\n\r\nIf you paid for any of the service that wasn't fit for purpose you will be able to claim a refund why is this not the same with our Road tax",
        "background": "We are paying road tax for roads that are not fit for us to drive on and this is causing damage to our vehicles and the cost lies with us the tax payer to repair our cars. if you are paying for a service the service that you are paying for sure be suitable and not value for money.",
